What you need to know:

The Safari will zoom off at midday outside the traditional starting point outside the Kenyatta International Convention Centre (KICC) for the first competitive section, the Kasarani Stadium Super Special Stage. where cars will race side by side.The dry weather conditions guarantee thrilling action on ends in a span of two hours of adrenaline-pumping rally pundits and the general public has never witnessed in this part of the world.